arriving soon enough after Carnation....

She landed ready for combat. Another time she wished she had her old style 
form. But, her claws extended, her fang showed. The only other thing was her 
tail... it still attached to her, she would not use it... not yet. 

Her clear blue optics glared at Rodimus. "Well, well.. Rodimus Prime. I'm 
rather surprised to see you... functioning! But.. that can easily be 
REMEDIED!" 

She leapt at Rodimus, ready to attack him in a vicious primal rage, her claws 
slashing at him.

--part1_162.1e35bd64.2bb910ec_boundary
